# Privacy Policy for VRCM

**Last Updated:** October 23, 2025

## 1. Introduction

Welcome to **VRCM**. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information in connection with your use of our application.

## 2. Data Collection

**We affirm that VRCM does NOT collect any personal data or user information.**

Specifically:

-  **No personal information** (name, email, address, etc.) is collected.
-  **No usage data** (app activity, diagnostics, etc.) is tracked or stored.
-  **No device identifiers** (IDFA, IDFV, advertising IDs) are accessed.
-  **No location data** is requested or recorded.
-  **No data is shared** with third parties.

## 3. Data Processing

All operations occur locally on your device. No data is transmitted to any servers or external services.

## 4. Children's Privacy

Our app does not collect data from anyone, including children under 13.

## 5. Changes to This Policy

If we ever change our data practices, we will update this policy and notify users.

## 6. Contact Us

If you have questions about this policy, contact us at:  
**kamosama.dev@gmail.com**
